* ============================================================
* CURSOR_FAMILY_REGRESSION_001.DTS
*
* Purpose:
*   Regression for core cursor/navigation commands after
*   nav-layer/order-iterator repairs.
*
* Scope:
*   - Physical (natural) order
*   - CNX ordered traversal
*   - TOP / BOTTOM
*   - GO / GOTO
*   - SKIP
*   - SEEK
*
* Notes:
*   - Uses AREA and SMARTLIST to verify position/order.
*   - Does not use LIST to prove TOP/BOTTOM or ordered movement.
*   - Assumes STUDENTS.dbf exists.
*   - Assumes STUDENTS.cnx exists with at least tags:
*         LNAME
*         FNAME
* ============================================================

SET ECHO OFF

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO CURSOR FAMILY REGRESSION 001
ECHO ============================================================

SET V32
WORKSPACE OPEN DBF
SELECT STUDENTS

ECHO --- SECTION 1: Physical baseline ---
SET ORDER TO 0
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 2: Physical TOP ---
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 3: Physical BOTTOM ---
BOTTOM
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 4: Physical GOTO absolute ---
GOTO 10
AREA
SMARTLIST 3

ECHO --- SECTION 5: Physical GO absolute ---
GO 25
AREA
SMARTLIST 3

ECHO --- SECTION 6: Physical GO TOP / GO BOTTOM ---
GO TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 3
GO BOTTOM
AREA
SMARTLIST 3

ECHO --- SECTION 7: Physical SKIP forward/backward ---
GO TOP
SKIP 5
AREA
SMARTLIST 3
SKIP -2
AREA
SMARTLIST 3

ECHO --- SECTION 8: Physical GO relative (+/-n) ---
GO TOP
GO +7
AREA
SMARTLIST 3
GO -3
AREA
SMARTLIST 3

ECHO --- SECTION 9: Physical boundary checks ---
GO TOP
SKIP -1
AREA
GO BOTTOM
SKIP 1
AREA

ECHO --- SECTION 10: Physical SEEK fallback behavior ---
SET ORDER TO 0
SEEK ANDERSON
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO --- CNX ORDERED TESTS ---
ECHO ============================================================

ECHO --- SECTION 11: Attach CNX / activate LNAME ---
SET INDEX TO STUDENTS.cnx
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
ASCEND
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 12: CNX TOP ascending ---
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 13: CNX BOTTOM ascending ---
BOTTOM
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 14: CNX GO TOP / GO BOTTOM ---
GO TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
GO BOTTOM
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 15: CNX SKIP under ordered traversal ---
GO TOP
SKIP 5
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
SKIP -2
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 16: CNX GO relative under ordered traversal ---
GO TOP
GO +8
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
GO -3
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 17: CNX boundary checks ascending ---
GO TOP
SKIP -1
AREA
GO BOTTOM
SKIP 1
AREA

ECHO --- SECTION 18: CNX GOTO absolute while ordered ---
GOTO 10
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 19: CNX SEEK on active tag LNAME ---
GO TOP
SEEK ANDERSON
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 20: CNX descending endpoints ---
DESCEND
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
BOTTOM
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 21: CNX descending relative movement ---
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
SKIP 3
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
SKIP -1
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 22: CNX boundary checks descending ---
TOP
SKIP -1
AREA
BOTTOM
SKIP 1
AREA

ECHO --- SECTION 23: CNX switch to FNAME tag ---
ASCEND
SET ORDER TO TAG FNAME
TOP
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 24: SEEK on active FNAME tag ---
SEEK ADRIEN
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 25: GO / SKIP on FNAME order ---
GO TOP
GO +6
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
SKIP -2
AREA
SMARTLIST 5
GO BOTTOM
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO --- SECTION 26: FNAME boundary checks ---
GO TOP
SKIP -1
AREA
GO BOTTOM
SKIP 1
AREA

ECHO ============================================================
ECHO --- CLEANUP / RETURN TO NATURAL ---
ECHO ============================================================

SET ORDER TO 0
AREA
SMARTLIST 5

ECHO CURSOR FAMILY REGRESSION COMPLETE
